         <div type="translation" ana="#b1" xml:id="zoor0282.translation" corresp="#zoor0282.transcription">
            <p>Monument of the blessed Ouales (Valens), (son) of Eusebios, who died having a
                    good name and good faith (at the age) of 48 years, in (the) year... one (the)
                    14th (day) [of (the) month... on (the)...day of (the) Lord]. [Be of good cheer],
                    no one (is) immortal. </p>
         </div>
